"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-21-keeping-cool-managing-emotions-cheering-olympic-heroes\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"AS Jamaica tunes in to the Olympic Games, excitement will fill the air.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 71, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999986415805456, \"rank\": 1.2490261024487676e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans will eagerly watch their favourite athletes compete on the grandest stage, but with high stakes come intense emotions.\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From joy to anxiety, cheering for our sports heroes can lead to an emotional roller coaster.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's how to manage those feelings and make the most of this thrilling experience, Jamaican style!\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.7084983575203305, \"rank\": 0.4114241640929433, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1) EMBRACE THE EMOTION  First and foremost, it's essential to accept that strong emotions are part of being a fan.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it's elation after a gold medal win or heartbreak from a narrow defeat, allow yourself to feel.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Acknowledging these emotions can enhance your viewing experience, making it more memorable and authentic.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2) CELEBRATE WITH SOUND  In Jamaica, the energy of watching sports often involves lively celebrations.\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999986415805456, \"rank\": 1.2490261024487676e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From blowing vuvuzelas to clanging pot covers, fans express their excitement with enthusiasm.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These sounds not only amplify the atmosphere but also serve as a great way to channel those emotions.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So grab your instruments and make some noise!\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3) PRACTISE MINDFULNESS  When the pressure mounts, mindfulness can help ground you.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take a few deep breaths before the event begins, focusing on the rhythm of your breath.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you start feeling overwhelmed during a competition, pause for a moment to refocus.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simple techniques, like counting to 10 or visualising a calm place, can reduce anxiety and keep you centred.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"4) SHARE THE EXPERIENCE  Watching the Olympics with friends or family can amplify the joy and lessen the stress.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share your excitement, discuss performances, and celebrate wins together.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The camaraderie of being with fellow fans provides support and makes the emotional journey more enjoyable.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And do not forget to bring out the drum or any musical instrument for that extra flair!\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"5) BALANCE YOUR VIEWING HABITS  While it's tempting to immerse yourself completely in Olympic coverage, consider balancing your viewing habits.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Set limits on how much time you spend glued to the screen.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Engaging in other activities, such as going for a walk or reading, can provide much-needed breaks and help manage heightened emotions.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"6) KEEP PERSPECTIVE  While it's easy to get caught up in the moment, remember that sports are unpredictable.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes train tirelessly, but outcomes are never guaranteed.\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keeping a healthy perspective allows you to appreciate the thrill of competition without becoming too emotionally invested in the results.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"7) REFLECT AND RELEASE  After an event, take a moment to reflect on your emotions.\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What made you feel joyful or anxious?\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Writing down your thoughts or discussing them with others can be therapeutic.\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Acknowledging and releasing these feelings can enhance your overall experience and prepare you for the next event.\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Olympic Games unfold, remember that while the competition brings highs and lows, managing your emotions can help you savour every moment.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So cheer loudly, clang those pot covers, blow your vuvuzelas, and enjoy the extraordinary journey of the Olympic spirit!\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Robiann Broomfield recently completed her PhD and has finished her clinical internship at Baylor College of Medicine/TIRR Memorial Hermann Hospital, where she focused on rehabilitation psychology and neuropsychology.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3072, \"end\": 3082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999999940082489, \"rank\": 5.863821481260605e-09, \"text\": \"Broomfield\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In September, she will further her expertise with a fellowship in neuropsychology at Harvard Medical School.\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3366, \"end\": 3388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_Medical_School\", \"score\": 0.9999996995484705, \"rank\": 3.0045179496379354e-07, \"text\": \"Harvard Medical School\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_Medical_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_Medical_School\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Broomfield is passionate about advancing mental health care and contributing to the understanding of cognitive processes in rehabilitation settings.\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999999940082489, \"rank\": 5.863821481260605e-09, \"text\": \"Broomfield\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3554, \"entities\": []}]}"